"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/773698","Department of Health","false","2017-11-01","<p>NHS England currently have no plans to collect centralised data to measure any reduction in the number of prescriptions for catheters, out-patient appointments, surgical interventions and costs relating to pads and other incontinence products.</p>","Winchester","Steve Brine",,"2017-11-01T12:02:21.04Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/773698/answer","Biography information for Steve Brine","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/773698/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/773698/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2017-10-19","Incontinence","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, pursuant to the Answer of 9 October 2017 to Question 9587, on incontinence, if he will make it his policy to collect centrally that information.","false","Biography information for Sir Mark Hendrick","Preston","Mr Mark Hendrick","108697"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/773867","Cabinet Office","false","2017-10-31","<p>As a result of recruitment issues the team held vacant positions for some time during FY16/17. These have now been resolved and the budget increase reflects the team’s build-up to full strength.</p><p>The Gulf Strategy Integrated Delivery team employs six full-time and one part-time Government employees. One is military and six civilian.</p>","Ashford","Damian Green","108658","2017-10-31T15:19:35.623Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/773867/answer","Biography information for Damian Green","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/773867/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/773867/answer","Ashford","Damian Green","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/773867/answer/previousversion/18018","Biography information for Damian Green","53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2017-10-19","Gulf Strategy Unit: Finance","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, with reference to the Answer of 19 October 2016 to Question 47638 and pursuant to the Answer of 12 October 2017 to Question 8077, for what reasons the budget for the Gulf Strategy Integrated Delivery Team has more than doubled in the last financial year.","false","Biography information for David Linden","Glasgow East","David Linden","108657"
